<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Welcome to {{nooriescornerApp.name}} - {{nooriescornerApp.slogan}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo img {
            max-width: 300px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="{{nooriescornerApp.logo}}" alt="Logo">
        </div>

        <p>Dear {{username}},</p>

        <p>Congratulations and a warm welcome to {{nooriescornerApp.name}}! We are excited to inform you that your
            account registration is now successfully completed. You are officially a valued member of our blouse-loving
            community.</p>

        <p>Now that you have joined us, get ready to explore an array of stylish blouses and discover the perfect ones
            that reflect your unique taste. Here's a quick overview of what you can do with your new account:</p>

        <ol>
            <li><u>Browse and Shop:</u> Dive into our captivating collection of blouses, featuring the latest trends,
                stunning designs, and an assortment of colors and sizes. Enjoy the convenience of shopping from the comfort of
                your own home.</li>
            <li><u>Create Your Wishlist:</u> Found a blouse you love but want to save it for later? Simply add it to
                your wishlist, and you can easily access and revisit your favorite items whenever you like.</li>
            <li><u>Personalize Your Profile:</u> Make your account truly yours by personalizing your profile. Upload a
                profile picture, update your preferences, and share your fashion inspirations with our community.</li>
            <li><u>Exclusive Offers and Updates:</u> As a valued member, you'll be among the first to hear about our
                exciting promotions, limited-time offers, and new blouse arrivals. Be sure to keep an eye on your inbox for our
                newsletters and updates.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>Should you need any assistance during your shopping journey, our dedicated customer support team is here to
            help. Feel free to reach out to us at
            <a href="mailto:{{nooriescornerApp.email}}">{{nooriescornerApp.email}}</a>, and we'll be more than happy to
            assist you.
        </p>

        <p>Once again, congratulations on becoming a member of {{nooriescornerApp.name}}. We can't wait to see you rock
            the latest blouse trends and showcase your unique style. Happy shopping!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>{{nooriescornerApp.name}} Team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>